subject: HISTORY
text: Give the century, B.C. or A.D., of each of the following, indicate who or what each was, and say why each is important in history: St. Augustine of Canterbury, the Murder of Thomas Becket, the Battle of Carham, the First Book of Discipline, Lord Lister, the Sailing of the Mayflower, Simon de Montfort, William Paterson.
